Package: live-migrator
Version: 2.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), python3, qemu-server, pve-manager, inotify-tools
Maintainer: Lagrange <lagrange@proxmox-cluster>
Description: Signal-driven migration orchestrator for Proxmox VE (v2)
 Reacts to signals from RAM, vCPU, and GPU agents via inotifywait.
 Supports MIGRATE_VM, LIGHTEN_NODE, GPU_REQUEST, and CONSOLIDATE_VM.
 Includes auto-placement, cluster harmonization, and maintenance mode.
